title: | Video | Is ABVP the new Khap Panchayat, asks JNU's Shehla Rashid on Ramjas violence | India Videos | - India Today
text:
Is ABVP the new Khap Panchayat, asks JNU's Shehla Rashid on Ramjas violence India Today Television | February 23, 2017 Next Video UP election politics explained through Rudyard Kipling's Jungle Book Embed Feedback 
Former JNUSU vice president Shela Rashid asks an important question on the ongoing violent clash in Delhi University's Ramjas college- Is ABVP the new Khap Panchayat? This comes after the right-wing students' union forced cancellation of Shela Rashid and Umar Khalid's lecture in a cultural programme and later embroiled in a violent clash with students protesting against this browbeating in an educational institute. Situation took a violent turn on Wednesday as the two groups clashed outside Maurice Nagar police station injuring many. Tension still prevails on the Delhi University's North Campus and the classes remain suspended. Next Video
